name: mikroe.click.gnss18
short_description: GNSS 18 Click is a compact add-on board designed for high-precision GNSS applications. This board features the SAM-M10Q-00B-00B, M10 standard precision GNSS module from u-blox, known for exceptional sensitivity and rapid acquisition of L1 GNSS signals. It supports concurrent reception of GPS, Galileo, GLONASS, and BeiDou B1C, with additional support for QZSS and SBAS. Featuring u-blox Super-S technology for improved dynamic position accuracy and low power consumption of 37mW in continuous tracking mode, it is ideal for battery-operated devices.
